  "message": "test(conformance): expand KEYS command edge case coverage\n\nAdd 21 comprehensive KEYS conformance tests:\n- Prefix/suffix wildcard patterns\n- Character class matching [ab] and [a-b]\n- Negated character class [^ab]\n- Question mark single-char matching\n- Escaped special characters (\\*, \\?, \\[, \\])\n- Expired keys filtering\n- Literal brackets in key names\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
